	<td><span class="topic">What do you spend a longer doing, programming or optimizing?</span><br /><span class="gensmall"><a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=6525">http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=6525</a></span></td>
